# 🌍 GeoAssist — AI-Powered Geographic Data Quality Framework on Databricks

> **GeoAssist is a reusable, configuration-driven framework that leverages Large Language Models (LLMs) to automatically detect, validate, and correct geographic data quality issues directly within Databricks.**
>
> Eliminate manual cleansing, reduce dependency on domain experts, and standardize geographic attributes such as cities, states, and countries at scale.

---

##  Why GeoAssist?

Geographic data quality issues are among the most common challenges in analytics and data engineering pipelines.

A simple typo can lead to:

* Broken joins across datasets
* Duplicate entities in reporting
* Inaccurate aggregations and dashboards
* Poor customer and operational insights

### Example Data Quality Issues

| Raw Value      | Correct Value  |
| -------------- | -------------- |
| Mumbay         | Mumbai         |
| Chenai         | Chennai        |
| New Yrok       | New York       |
| Untied Kingdom | United Kingdom |
| Germaany       | Germany        |

Traditionally, resolving these issues requires:

* Complex rule-based transformations
* Large reference mapping tables
* Continuous maintenance
* Geographic domain expertise

GeoAssist replaces these approaches with an AI-powered validation framework built on Databricks.

---

## 🏗️ Solution Architecture

```text
                    ┌──────────────────┐
                    │   Raw Geo Data   │
                    └────────┬─────────┘
                             │
                             ▼
                    ┌──────────────────┐
                    │  Bronze Layer    │
                    │ Raw Ingestion    │
                    └────────┬─────────┘
                             │
                             ▼
                    ┌──────────────────┐
                    │ Geo Validator    │
                    │ Llama 3.3 70B    │
                    └────────┬─────────┘
                             │
                             ▼
                    ┌──────────────────┐
                    │ Confidence Score │
                    └────────┬─────────┘
                             │
         ┌───────────────────┼───────────────────┐
         ▼                   ▼                   ▼
 ┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐
 │ High Conf.  │    │ Medium Conf.│    │ Low Conf.   │
 │ Auto Fix    │    │ Review      │    │ Manual QA   │
 └──────┬──────┘    └──────┬──────┘    └──────┬──────┘

```

---

## ✨ Key Features

### AI-Powered Geographic Validation

Uses Databricks Foundation Models (Llama 3.3 70B) to:

* Detect spelling errors
* Identify invalid geographic values
* Suggest standardized corrections
* Generate confidence scores

### ⚙️ Configuration-Driven

No code changes required.

```python
TARGET_COLUMNS = [
    "city",
    "state",
    "country"
]
```

Simply update the target columns to match your source dataset.


### Confidence-Based Routing

Records are automatically classified into:

| Confidence Level | Action                      |
| ---------------- | --------------------------- |
| High             | Auto-corrected and promoted |
| Medium           | Sent for business review    |
| Low              | Requires manual validation  |

### 🔄 Reusable Across Domains

GeoAssist can be applied to:

* Customer Master Data
* CRM Systems
* Sales Platforms
* Logistics Data
* Supply Chain Data
* Vendor Management Systems
* Operational Data Stores

