| ---------------- | ----------- | ------------------------- |
| airports.dat.txt | OpenFlights | Raw airport location data |
| cities500.txt    | GeoNames    | Geographic reference data |

### Storage Location

```text
/Volumes/geo_assist/raw/geo_assist/
```

---

## 🔧 Getting Started

### 1. Upload Your Dataset

Place your file inside a Unity Catalog Volume.

### 2. Configure Target Columns

```python
TARGET_COLUMNS = [
    "city",
    "state",
    "country"
]
```

### 3. Update Input Path

```python
INPUT_FILE = "/Volumes/geo_assist/raw/your_file.csv"
```

### 4. Run the Pipeline

```text
01_bronze.ipynb
        ↓
validator.ipynb
        ↓
02_silver.ipynb
        ↓
03_gold.ipynb
```

That's it.

GeoAssist automatically validates, standardizes, and publishes a trusted geographic dataset.

